======================================================================

python-aiohttp-socks (Proxy (HTTP, SOCKS) connector for aiohttp)

The aiohttp-socks package provides a proxy connector for aiohttp.
It Supports SOCKS4(a), SOCKS5(h), HTTP (CONNECT) as well as Proxy
chains. It uses python-socks for core proxy functionality.

HOME: 

======================================================================
REQUIRES: python-aiohttp 

